{"tid":1469423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"機場嘅事你地到底明唔明呀!!","createTime":"2019-08-14T01:47:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T09:15:43.000Z","uid":12409,"like":16,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"dc6bb81d87bf5a849458bf72779f8e65a9b7ea39","tid":1469423,"uid":12409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:47:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>不割蓆唔係得個講字</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n大家812突擊去機場和理非咗一日<br />\n就覺得好成功   好開心咁打晒飛機<br />\n到第二日對家一出招就食晒屎咁<br />\n<br />\n由一朝頭早開始屌手足係機場阻人上機<br />\n到夜晚屌手足圍大陸狗 阻醫護救人<br />\n又開始拉起一條道德底線出嚟<br />\n依樣唔好做 嗰樣會失民心<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">大家一早講好咗嘅團結 不分化 去咗邊</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n論暴力嘅程度<br />\n對比起黑警所做嘅又算得啲咩<br />\n我地受傷嘅 所失去嘅<br />\n無論睇到定睇唔到<br />\n真係太多太多<br />\n<br />\n<strong>大家係機場大聲嗌黑警還眼<br />\n真係嗌完就算?</strong><br />\n唔係叫大家要去勇武<br />\n但講好咗兄弟爬山<br />\n前線捉咗咁有力嘅大陸狗 <br />\n依一樣有力度嘅籌碼<br />\n圍住唔放人走 唔俾醫護帶走佢<br />\n依啲都係前線嘅決定<br />\n<br />\nBe Water <br />\n唔單單係走位be water<br />\n講嘅係連個人嘅思想、現場嘅決定都需要be water <br />\n<strong>現場嘅人若水 就相信現場</strong><br />\n<br />\n就係知道身邊會有大量鬼<br />\n正正係咁先更需要企硬同團結<br />\n如果我地係咁容易被分化<br />\n大家對自己嘅目標都唔係咁堅定嘅時候<br />\n我地就只係一盆散沙<br />\n有鬼浦晒上面嘅咪捉佢<br />\n捉唔到嘅鬼 我地咪團結到包實佢<br />\n記住初衷<br />\n記住個目標 堅定咁行過去<br />\n<strong>唔係現場嘅人請若水 相信大家做嘅野係岩</strong><br />\n<br />\n其實我知大家都驚<br />\n大家一開始驚惡法 驚中共<br />\n驚輸 <br />\n驚比人拉<br />\n驚失去一啲重要嘅野 重要嘅人  <br />\n<br />\n人最大嘅弱點就係恐懼<br />\n對未知嘅恐懼 對未來嘅恐懼<br />\n但只要克服恐懼<br />\n未知就可以係一個希望<br />\n<br />\n依場運動<br />\n如果我地咁快已經打定輸數 <br />\n咁仲行出嚟為咩  早啲返屋企瞓覺啦<br />\n然後醒返 <br />\n只會一直比人打壓 迫害<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n大家五年前已經失敗過一次啦<br />\n你地問心仲有幾多次可以輸<br />\n你地甘心咩<br />\n<br />\n<strong>總之<br />\n唔撚割    <br />\n做乜撚都唔撚割</strong>"},{"pid":"1661b2286e36c740d9c8066fc88fcfd3895bd89b","tid":1469423,"uid":11143,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:47:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"24b2685c701c01bd177cfb41a30a753695dcb273","tid":1469423,"uid":95487,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:48:15.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有，唔會捉得晒<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">今次捉到既鬼唔會係第一隻<br />\n更加唔會係最後一隻</span><br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理優都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">818見！五大訴求，缺一不可！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a3ea37af01fce216c90927296524b63b24d758d","tid":1469423,"uid":293698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:49:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ca61bf738e72cf16314493d912b6ab1969d43075","tid":1469423,"uid":12409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a3ea37af01fce216c90927296524b63b24d758d","tid":1469423,"uid":293698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:49:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:03:50.000Z","msg":"根本唔使刻意去捉<br />\n極明顯捉得到嘅鬼當然要捉 <br />\n割鬼要割得快<br />\n<br />\n但捉唔到 唔肯定嘅時候<br />\n佢地就係手足"},{"pid":"61e586e47d2e620ac941e2e260c53448dd3dbf35","tid":1469423,"uid":293698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:04:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cc1efdd2429fadfff3e47bbcea11634f8c8af685","tid":1469423,"uid":6777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:07:39.000Z","msg":"機管局說，任何人亦不得在機場出席或參與任何在機管局<span style=\"color: red;\">指定地方之外舉行的示威</span>、抗議或公眾活動<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">麻煩大家睇清楚呢句，唔好比人帶風向！</span>"},{"pid":"dcbedd802e47083056eb8361e255e7181aba74ea","tid":1469423,"uid":283425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:10:33.000Z","msg":"好多新聞只會報，市民只會睇到：<br />\n<strong>暴徒圍毆送機客</strong><br />\n<br />\n其實影完相 攞曬證據咪算"},{"pid":"f815d9c56456c48ef494745026310f87eee818e4","tid":1469423,"uid":12409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:40:00.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"00441e7f94174c5fbdbe1fde0827e38e13e244ca","tid":1469423,"uid":12409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:49:21.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"831a85be1f4b8443d7c9f675d57c4677cbce346c","tid":1469423,"uid":12409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:01:13.000Z","msg":"自推3"},{"pid":"de53269c5271ffc733cde6e598abd14946f4e5a0","tid":1469423,"uid":12409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:59:35.000Z","msg":"自推4"},{"pid":"5e4f7d1b01ddd81db872eed9c8aa37e5107a34de","tid":1469423,"uid":37894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:00:23.000Z","msg":"我地應該每星期搵一日，同一個時間一齊搭車入機場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468945\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468945</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"eada691b3d4df7c3659e046b87d31930f20d05ff","tid":1469423,"uid":12409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:14:53.000Z","msg":"自推一個十連就收皮"},{"pid":"272f8830ab06770dd7a8ef5fd0aef85d97787cb1","tid":1469423,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:15:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fa8eb885a01491fe226a5fdad4a1b7371640b06","tid":1469423,"uid":18728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:15:39.000Z","msg":"3毛日日搵嘢互屌, 建議巴絲睇post由第2-3頁開始, 同埋推返有用post上嚟<br />\n連登仔女咁醒目一定識分"},{"pid":"9446417652ef17948c911c17c13e73e3f1caed3a","tid":1469423,"uid":87541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:15:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五點拆局建議（強調係官、警、黨一手造成）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1470088\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1470088</a></span>"},{"pid":"1981b85658d248da65d1560d4eee00d975b62bb0","tid":1469423,"uid":12409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:22:48.000Z","msg":"十連_1"},{"pid":"2ad44795516692caaa0998cebd75887acc137d7e","tid":1469423,"uid":12409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:26:29.000Z","msg":"十連_2"},{"pid":"7b2212f861bacccc22a419099c35628a4b3c4c60","tid":1469423,"uid":35364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:27:56.000Z","msg":"捉到共狗又唔想就咁放走，<br />\n用幽默手法嘲諷羞辱就夠，<br />\n貼住「平反六四」罰坐，<br />\n破壞證件、報名參軍之類，<br />\n顯得有文化又收威嚇之用。<br />\n<br />\n懲罰並唔一定要流血，<br />\n有時只需要取其象徵意義。<br />\n檯底點懲治黑警都無所謂，<br />\n但檯面一定要好好睇睇。<br />\n<br />\n【反省與建議】「俘虜」處置提案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468537\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468537</a>"},{"pid":"6adfceda6dfbcac7dd149fc50f950e1a5d3a265b","tid":1469423,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:28:57.000Z","msg":"陳雲：<br />\n做錯事不道歉，是違反道德的啊。這個當然，但我們不是在小學課室，由班長和班主任裁判，我們是在戰場上，警察、法官、電視台、報紙、觀眾都是中共的人。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你道歉，對方就有材料展開政治謠言宣傳，而且要求你再為其他你無做過的事道歉（例如毆打北京記者），之後你拒絕，他們就向你開火射擊。</span></span>做錯了事就馬上走，不是道歉！<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">普選勝利了，在民選元首認為安全的情況</span></span>，才為以往的錯失道歉，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">道歉也是元首來做，不是民眾來做</span></span>，賠償也是用政府的錢，不是民間眾籌。"},{"pid":"d2ed58d44e78ef1d04f42547deb2e960bab08bf5","tid":1469423,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:30:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"59e5cc2615b4ca569ed668b128bdd2f03b4fe153","tid":1469423,"uid":25147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:06:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"03540c239efece5dbc50ada93ef1e1c7faf6528c","tid":1469423,"uid":25147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:07:11.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"13060208275db3d19e5115f4bb0e2640860ff1a1","tid":1469423,"uid":25147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:07:24.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"53bc78c4c4c65ba0283fb862c1822be0f3c2313b","tid":1469423,"uid":25147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:07:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"379f9e111e82544b890809b50229e2861a8a3519","tid":1469423,"uid":25147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:08:09.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"48cd0df28c9d571fe7facd26cdd9e2ffe0c521e0","tid":1469423,"uid":25147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:08:29.000Z","msg":"811"},{"pid":"bfa8cbd4302925fa3367e6c8de4ec095f05229a1","tid":1469423,"uid":25147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:08:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9ec01b715a62b47ed7d32866493b215eec0da34a","tid":1469423,"uid":25147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:09:45.000Z","msg":"10連"},{"pid":"9716f93fd8c08cc99a4f5af6e9e2294eb8ae7313","tid":1469423,"uid":25147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:09:56.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"c46fb147deb91909ad76b8c1729b1f3c6c804921","tid":1469423,"uid":25147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:10:10.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"a1b6b815e941b5ebc9f9dfe46303a48f3599502b","tid":1469423,"uid":25147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:10:23.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"60af9701d599ddb35c2d4b4d54fafc0d1bbc7a1a","tid":1469423,"uid":12409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ec01b715a62b47ed7d32866493b215eec0da34a","tid":1469423,"uid":25147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:09:45.000Z","msg":"10連"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:10:25.000Z","msg":"唔好快過我十連"},{"pid":"095edfa0fd82b5343153ebc6dc8ff81e88553b64","tid":1469423,"uid":25147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:10:37.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"3674e7b9ed60f9c83f53589c49a9d2b0701cdc3c","tid":1469423,"uid":25147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:10:50.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"c5d2d948e08db2a10fc5fff965692077d6de8bee","tid":1469423,"uid":25147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:11:00.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"651677b4bb295d3eb1acbcdca72fa895ad132917","tid":1469423,"uid":25147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:11:10.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"ff2481065f8f9195f2b9064c0d5fb61f53c10eee","tid":1469423,"uid":25147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:11:23.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"a38c7b537e2228ea1ec70853db94fa6efaef0701","tid":1469423,"uid":25147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:11:36.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"037d077a421a0f412f2c4f807bfe74599e3b34a8","tid":1469423,"uid":25147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:11:57.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"96f19681818222cb0e676a61c45ffac1c705e33f","tid":1469423,"uid":25147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:12:08.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"8f2b8928